title: The One Where We Have To Be Nice (Re-Release)
description:
This is a re-release of one of Bob and Monét's favorite episodes from this year. Tune in to hear this ICONIC episode where Bob hates on Colleen, Monét brings out their Birthday sweater, and Bob and Monét try to be nice to each other.
